source.name: School Attendance Statistics
source.description: Attendance data reflect what has been reported via our Period Attendance Reporting (PAR) process. As additional data is reported, it will be reflected in subsequent postings. Monthly data can change as new data is reported, and overall register numbers are expected to decrease each year once audited numbers are finalized. CBOs not included. Register statistics are unaudited and unofficial.
